# hexastral-app — LEGACY (retired omnibus)

**Status:** Retired per [ADR-0009](../../docs/decisions/0009-two-layer-matrix.md). Do not add new features here.

**Rules for any work in this directory:**
1. **Mobile patterns** → root [`.cursorrules`](../../.cursorrules) §3 (satellite apps)
2. **API / Workers** → [`apps/hexastral-api/.cursorrules`](../hexastral-api/.cursorrules)
3. **Architecture** → [`docs/ROADMAP.md`](../../docs/ROADMAP.md)

Launch-target apps live under `apps/auspice-app`, `apps/kindred-app`, etc. See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).
